data.description: Lightly lived in 6 year old Castlerock 1 story home with 3 Bedrooms 2 Bathrooms plus an OFFICE as a 4th room. Home is on a CUL DE SAC & GREEN BELT lot. Private back yard! You'll love this kitchen: GAS stove cooking, Granite countertops, Kitchen Island, stainless steel refrigerator. Relax under your COVERED front porch or COVERED wrap around back patio. Gutters, Sprinklers & water softener. Summary of upgrades & features: Granite Kitchen Countertops, Ceiling Fans, Gutters, Covered Front Porch, Covered Wrap Around Back Patio, Water Softener, High Ceilings, Community POOL, Jogging Trails, Fitness Center & playground. Popular Schertz, Cibolo, UC school district. Convenient to Joint Base Randolph, Fort Sam Houston & New Braunfels. Come see us in Schertz at 6805 Concho Creek.
